---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Terms of Service',
  description: 'Terms of Service for SellOnTube — the YouTube content strategy and production service for B2B businesses.',
  robots: { index: true, follow: true },
};

const lastUpdated = '6 March 2026';
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-10">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Overview</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of the website at
            <a href="https://sellontube.com" class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline">sellontube.com</a>
            and any services provided by SellOnTube ("we", "us", "our").
            By accessing or using our site, you agree to these Terms. If you do not agree, do not use the site.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-3">
            SellOnTube provides YouTube content strategy, production, and distribution services for B2B businesses.
            Specific terms for paid engagements are set out in a separate service agreement provided when you become a client.
            These Terms govern use of the website and any free resources available on it.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2. Use of the site</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">You may use this site for lawful purposes only. You agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorised access to any part of the site or its infrastructure</li>
            <li>Use automated tools to scrape, copy, or index site content without our written permission</li>
            <li>Transmit any malicious code, spam, or disruptive material</li>
            <li>Misrepresent your identity or affiliation with any person or organisation</li>
            <li>Use the site in any way that violates applicable laws or regulations</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">3. Intellectual property</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            All content on this site — including text, graphics, logos, images, blog posts, tools, and page layouts —
            is owned by or licensed to SellOnTube and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-3">
            You may read, share links to, and quote brief excerpts from our content for personal or editorial use,
            provided you attribute SellOnTube and link back to the original page. You may not reproduce, republish,
            or commercialise our content in full without our written permission.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">4. No professional or legal advice</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            Content on this site — including blog posts, calculators, and strategy guides — is for informational
            purposes only. It does not constitute legal, financial, tax, or professional advice.
            Results described or implied are illustrative and not guaranteed. Your outcomes will depend on
            your business, offer, market, and execution.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">5. Third-party links</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            Our site may link to third-party websites, tools, or services. These links are provided for convenience.
            We do not control third-party sites and are not responsible for their content, accuracy, or practices.
            Visiting a linked site is at your own risk.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">6. Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            This site and its content are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied.
            We do not warrant that the site will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses or other
            harmful components. We make no representations about the accuracy or completeness of any content.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">7. Limitation of liability</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, SellOnTube shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental,
            consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of, or inability to use, this site or its content.
            Our total liability for any claim arising from your use of the site is limited to the amount you
            paid us in the 3 months preceding the claim, or INR 1,000 (whichever is greater).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">8. Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            Your use of this site is also governed by our
            <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>,
            which is incorporated into these Terms by reference.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">9. Changes to these Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            We may update these Terms from time to time. Changes take effect when posted on this page.
            The "Last updated" date at the top reflects the most recent revision.
            Continued use of the site after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">10. Governing law</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            These Terms are governed by the laws of India. Any disputes arising from these Terms or your
            use of the site shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts located in India.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">11. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            Questions about these Terms? Email us at
            <a href="mailto:hello@sellontube.com" class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline">hello@sellontube.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
